@sig bc925d79
export getDBSchema(t)→e,a.map,a.reduce|read parsed project to list all defined SQL tables and columns
export getTableUsage(a,s)→e,t,readers.some,readers.push,writers.some,writers.push|find readers and writers for tables using parsed graph edges
export getDBDeadTables(a)→e,t,r.add,r.has,o.filter,collectReferencedColumns|find schema tables not referenced by any read/write in code
collectReferencedColumns(e)→t.add|heuristically collect all potential column names from code
PATTERNS: dependency graph analysis|heuristic DB column extraction
EDGE_CASES: hardcoded standard columns prevent false positive dead tables
